WEBVTT

07:16.083 --> 07:19.292
Thank you very much.

08:01.633 --> 08:05.925
I bow to all the seekers of truth!

08:14.101 --> 08:19.851
It is to be understood that truth is what it is.

08:21.143 --> 08:25.725
We cannot conceptualize it.

08:34.476 --> 08:36.642
We cannot achieve it

08:36.851 --> 08:40.684
by our human efforts or mental projections.

08:45.393 --> 08:51.393
We have to reach into a higher state to know it,

08:53.809 --> 08:55.976
to know it.

08:58.976 --> 09:03.059
The song that they sung just now,

09:03.351 --> 09:08.059
was written in the year sixteen hundred in India,

09:08.268 --> 09:12.226
by a very famous poet, Namadeva,

09:12.434 --> 09:15.434
who was a tailor.

09:18.725 --> 09:20.851
Loudly.

09:27.101 --> 09:29.892
In the sixteenth century.

09:33.143 --> 09:37.560
And they have been singing the song in the villages of India,

09:38.476 --> 09:41.476
with the same folk tune.

09:50.641 --> 09:52.976
It says that

09:53.184 --> 09:57.476
“I will ask for Yoga, that is the union with the Divine,

09:57.642 --> 09:59.809
from Mother”.

10:05.560 --> 10:10.393
"Ai" is the Mother. “I’ll ask the Mother to give me the Yoga”.

10:15.476 --> 10:19.184
And the “Ude, ude Ambe!” means that

10:19.393 --> 10:25.518
“O, Mother Kundalini, please rise, ude, ude, please rise!

10:35.560 --> 10:38.226
So this knowledge of our roots was known

10:38.434 --> 10:40.641
to many people all over the world,

10:40.809 --> 10:44.642
especially in India, to many saints.

10:58.017 --> 11:03.641
This Namadeva once went to meet another saint,

11:03.809 --> 11:09.143
who was a potter, making things out of clay.

11:17.641 --> 11:20.767
His name was Gora.

11:22.309 --> 11:25.143
He saw him and then he says,

11:25.351 --> 11:28.892
in very beautiful couplet he describes

11:29.101 --> 11:32.393
this personality of a potter.

11:41.601 --> 11:44.601
He says, “I came here,

11:46.725 --> 11:53.017
to see the formless,  that is this All-pervading Power.

11:54.143 --> 11:58.351
But I see It  in person, in form.”

12:14.059 --> 12:18.725
And he embraced with great joy!

12:23.518 --> 12:26.767
This is the acknowledgement.

12:26.976 --> 12:31.892
This is the knowledge of a saint about another saint.

12:38.393 --> 12:41.393
There is no jealousy,

12:41.642 --> 12:44.518
there is no competition,

12:44.684 --> 12:49.268
there is no knowledge to be asked about the person.

12:52.434 --> 12:55.976
Just through this

12:56.601 --> 13:00.809
emission of vibrations, of cool breeze of the Holy Ghost,

13:05.641 --> 13:08.934
you can understand who is the saint.

13:13.601 --> 13:17.017
So the time has come for us to know the truth.

13:17.268 --> 13:19.101
I call it the “Blossom time”,

13:19.309 --> 13:22.892
when there are so many people who are seeking the truth.

13:36.393 --> 13:41.184
Of course, it’s a living process of a living energy

13:41.393 --> 13:43.601
of living God.

13:49.934 --> 13:54.641
You cannot pay for anything that is living process.

13:58.351 --> 14:01.934
Like we sprout a seed in the Mother Earth,

14:02.309 --> 14:06.184
your Kundalini sprouts, spontaneously.

14:14.560 --> 14:18.725
And you get the blessings of the Divine Power.

14:23.351 --> 14:26.351
It is an All-pervading divine Power,

14:26.560 --> 14:30.101
about which all the Scriptures have talked.

14:38.393 --> 14:43.642
Essence of all the religions is that, "seek the Eternal".

14:49.268 --> 14:52.892
And transitory, is to be treated, with understanding,

14:53.101 --> 14:56.101
in its own limitations.

15:07.184 --> 15:11.268
But, when we see the problems of

15:11.476 --> 15:14.184
religion and religious people,

15:14.393 --> 15:18.143
we start wondering, what is this all about?

15:26.767 --> 15:31.934
One may be a Hindu, Christian, Muslim, any religion,

15:32.184 --> 15:35.976
commits any sin, there is no bounding on him.

15:51.393 --> 15:56.434
Nobody says, that “See, I am of this religion,

15:56.641 --> 15:59.641
I can’t commit this mistake”.

16:10.642 --> 16:13.642
Then on one side you see the fanaticism.

16:18.101 --> 16:21.684
And another side, you see people criticizing God

16:22.309 --> 16:26.059
and all the great prophets,

16:31.601 --> 16:34.601
because they don’t understand Divinity.

16:37.476 --> 16:43.476
And this has lead to a great confusion in this modern times.

16:48.809 --> 16:52.684
So, we have to ascend and know the Absolute

16:57.976 --> 17:00.976
and the absolute truth.

17:03.143 --> 17:05.725
In the West, as you see,

17:05.934 --> 17:08.725
we have so many modern things,

17:08.934 --> 17:13.351
and we have evolved like a tree outside.

17:22.309 --> 17:25.309
But we do not know our roots.

17:26.518 --> 17:31.309
Unless and until the tree knows the roots,

17:34.351 --> 17:38.601
there is always a danger of its destruction.

17:39.268 --> 17:42.434
That’s why we have problems today of ecology.

17:43.268 --> 17:49.434
We have problems of AIDS, drugs, all other extreme things.

18:03.434 --> 18:06.434
We have no balance.

18:08.393 --> 18:13.059
Machines we make, they are for us, we are not for machines.

18:21.059 --> 18:25.101
We discovered science for us, not for science.

18:29.476 --> 18:32.684
We are the masters.

18:33.184 --> 18:38.351
Why should there be problems within us and without?

18:44.684 --> 18:47.684
Also we find we are not integrated.

18:53.560 --> 18:58.641
There is a very little problem, that is,

18:58.809 --> 19:01.809
we do not know the Absolute.

19:07.641 --> 19:12.767
And Absolute is the truth for everyone.

19:17.934 --> 19:21.976
You become part and parcel of the whole.

19:27.393 --> 19:30.641
The microcosm becomes the macrocosm.

19:34.268 --> 19:37.059
Like this hand feels the pain

19:37.268 --> 19:40.434
and another just comes to soothe it,

19:40.641 --> 19:43.976
automatically, spontaneously.

19:53.268 --> 19:56.601
This hand doesn’t give pain to this hand.

19:56.851 --> 19:59.934
does not want to hurt it.

20:05.226 --> 20:09.268
This transformation has to take place among human beings.

20:13.518 --> 20:17.434
Then all barriers will drop and dissolve.

20:24.101 --> 20:28.351
And we’ll realize that we are created by one Creator,

20:31.851 --> 20:35.560
and the whole world is One.

20:36.101 --> 20:43.017
But just by having foundations of peace,

20:43.226 --> 20:45.934
foundations of cooperation,

20:46.143 --> 20:50.476
is all mental. It's not going to help us.

21:03.059 --> 21:06.518
This transformation has to take within ourselves,

21:06.725 --> 21:09.725
to solve our problems.

21:14.851 --> 21:18.684
But as a result of this happening, you are empowered

21:18.892 --> 21:23.767
that you can give Realizations to others and transform others.

21:34.892 --> 21:37.684
You are empowered that you can cure others

21:37.892 --> 21:41.143
and you can give comfort to others.

21:46.268 --> 21:49.309
You are empowered that you can council others

21:49.518 --> 21:52.601
about reality.

21:59.518 --> 22:03.725
Above all, you become peace yourself.

22:07.809 --> 22:09.809
You feel your peace

22:10.017 --> 22:14.226
and wherever you go, you emit peace and bliss.

22:19.393 --> 22:22.767
You become joy,

22:23.268 --> 22:26.393
and wherever you go, you emit joy.

22:28.642 --> 22:33.393
Joy, which has no duality of unhappiness and happiness.

22:37.725 --> 22:41.268
It seems fantastic.

22:41.560 --> 22:44.518
But human beings are fantastic.

22:46.101 --> 22:49.226
They don’t know their glory, they are not aware of it.

22:53.351 --> 22:57.017
Say, for example, this instrument is not put to the mains,

22:57.226 --> 23:00.184
it has no meaning.

23:06.101 --> 23:08.309
People are trying to find their meanings.

23:08.518 --> 23:11.393
First get connected to the whole.

23:18.641 --> 23:22.976
One has to make connected to this All-pervading Power,

23:23.184 --> 23:28.268
which is a subtle power, which does all living things.

23:39.892 --> 23:42.601
We see the flowers and we see

23:42.767 --> 23:46.892
that the trees have different fruits.

23:47.101 --> 23:50.309
Who does the choices and who makes all that?

24:04.059 --> 24:06.767
Just look at our eyes itself,

24:07.017 --> 24:10.560
are the best camera as that you could think of.

24:15.393 --> 24:19.518
We are already programmed to be a computer.

24:19.684 --> 24:22.684
We don’t think, it just works.

24:28.684 --> 24:32.101
But now you have to become the divine computer.

24:37.393 --> 24:40.017
Unless and until that happens,

24:40.226 --> 24:45.518
we'll have all the problems and more problems and more problems.

24:53.184 --> 24:56.518
So, we have to be that powerful personality,

24:56.684 --> 25:00.976
that compassionate personality, that dynamic personality.

25:08.725 --> 25:10.892
And powerful.

25:12.767 --> 25:16.143
And you should know all about your powers, too.

25:19.976 --> 25:23.268
All this is absolutely easy.

25:26.351 --> 25:29.642
We have lots of time, we have watches on,

25:29.851 --> 25:33.476
to save the time, but where do we waste it?

25:38.476 --> 25:40.851
If we could say,

25:41.268 --> 25:45.851
if you could spend some time on ourselves,

25:51.059 --> 25:53.976
then we don’t even need a watch. It works.

25:57.601 --> 25:59.725
And then you enter into the Kingdom of God,

25:59.934 --> 26:02.059
which is miraculous.

26:06.641 --> 26:10.684
And miracles of every kind, you see and you are amazed.

26:15.684 --> 26:18.976
So many here are Sahaja Yogis, all over the world.

26:19.184 --> 26:21.892
It is working now in thirty nations.

26:22.101 --> 26:27.268
And they all can tell you so many miracles.

26:40.641 --> 26:42.976
In India... All right.

26:45.809 --> 26:50.393
In India we have the University of Delhi,

26:50.601 --> 26:54.809
which has recognized Sahaja Yoga, for the course of MD

26:55.017 --> 26:57.476
and three doctors have submitted

26:57.642 --> 27:00.851
their thesis for it and have got it through.

27:05.518 --> 27:07.892
For doctors.

27:15.851 --> 27:20.434
And they have done subjects like physical fitness,

27:20.641 --> 27:24.017
and psychosomatic diseases like cancer,

27:24.809 --> 27:27.518
and thirdly, epilepsy.

27:33.059 --> 27:35.393
Psychosomatic.

27:37.393 --> 27:42.059
And physical, physical abilities, physical fitness.

27:45.976 --> 27:52.268
So it is for us to know about oneself

27:53.476 --> 27:56.684
and to enjoy ourselves and others.

28:07.309 --> 28:09.601
It is not frivolous

28:10.725 --> 28:13.725
and it is not serious.

28:14.351 --> 28:18.518
It is mirth and joy, mirth.

28:22.434 --> 28:24.434
What is mirth Mother?

28:24.601 --> 28:26.809
Mirth is fun.

28:27.017 --> 28:30.059
No word in French?

28:31.268 --> 28:35.725
I’m sorry, so now we'll have to introduce new word in French.

28:48.560 --> 28:51.184
When I first came on My program,

28:51.434 --> 28:54.684
I had one Sahaja Yogini in London,

28:54.892 --> 28:56.934
and when I first came, she told Me that,

28:57.143 --> 29:00.309
“Mother, You should not smile at all,

29:00.642 --> 29:06.560
because French think that life is all misery”.

29:26.351 --> 29:31.017
And that, ”If you do not feel sorry,

29:31.309 --> 29:33.184
then they’ll think you are ignoramus,

29:33.393 --> 29:36.393
you don’t know anything about the world.”

29:37.725 --> 29:40.309
Ignoramus, ignorant.

29:43.184 --> 29:46.976
No, no, no, that I am a ignoramus, if I'm not miserable.

29:58.934 --> 30:02.560
I'd read a novel of Victor Hugo, “Les miserable”,

30:02.725 --> 30:06.476
and I started with that to them, "dear les miserable".

30:11.184 --> 30:14.226
So that is not so.

30:15.226 --> 30:18.017
The Creator, who has created this creation,

30:18.226 --> 30:21.309
will never allow it to be destroyed.

30:27.268 --> 30:31.892
He has created you, also, so beautifully, so carefully,

30:32.101 --> 30:35.309
and everything is laid down within you.

30:45.059 --> 30:48.184
Whatever may be the past, please forget it.

30:51.268 --> 30:54.393
And the future doesn’t exist.

30:55.393 --> 30:59.226
In the present you all are going to get your Self-Realization.

31:03.143 --> 31:07.684
May God bless you all!

31:09.809 --> 31:12.725
Should I ask them to ask questions or something?

31:15.143 --> 31:18.434
Because that it prolongs a lot. What do you say?

31:20.226 --> 31:22.641
I should ask? All right.

31:22.809 --> 31:25.851
Now, if you want to ask Me some questions, please do.

31:26.059 --> 31:30.226
But by asking questions and knowing the answers,

31:30.434 --> 31:33.434
the Kundalini does not rise.

31:54.143 --> 31:57.268
I am telling you the truth.

31:59.226 --> 32:02.309
If you have any questions, you can ask Me.

32:07.226 --> 32:09.976
[unclear]

32:15.725 --> 32:18.268
It seems to be all interested of their Realization, Mother.

32:18.518 --> 32:21.518
No question?

32:24.892 --> 32:27.892
There's one gentleman there.

32:35.684 --> 32:39.684
He is saying, do You think, Mother, that the technique of Japa

32:39.892 --> 32:41.851
is very good for Self-Realization?

32:42.059 --> 32:44.601
No, my child, no.

32:47.309 --> 32:51.976
You see, the Japa is,

32:53.684 --> 32:58.226
they give you some name or something to recite.

32:59.560 --> 33:03.351
Now, it’s like a car.

33:05.309 --> 33:08.309
If it is ignited,

33:09.767 --> 33:13.725
if it is ignited and when it starts moving,

33:13.934 --> 33:17.184
you know where is the obstruction.

33:32.101 --> 33:34.934
Supposing I am in London,

33:35.143 --> 33:38.184
and I have to come to Paris.

33:39.101 --> 33:42.059
Now, on the way, I’ve not moved out at all.

33:42.268 --> 33:44.684
Sitting in London if I say

33:44.892 --> 33:48.684
“Open the door of Paris”, what is the use?

34:02.351 --> 34:05.184
Like the Kundalini has to rise.

34:05.393 --> 34:08.309
And passes through six centers.

34:08.518 --> 34:11.642
And any center, which is closed,

34:11.851 --> 34:16.725
that you can find out, we can find out, they can find out.

34:17.641 --> 34:20.684
Then we'll we have to of course

34:21.017 --> 34:23.434
say something which I will show you, just now,

34:23.601 --> 34:25.976
during meditation, just now,

34:26.226 --> 34:31.017
while your Kundalini will be rising. But the Kundalini must act.

34:56.434 --> 34:58.892
Moreover...

34:59.809 --> 35:04.434
Moreover, supposing I want to meet Mr. Mitterrand, all right?

35:07.560 --> 35:09.725
Now, for meeting him,

35:09.934 --> 35:13.393
supposing I go to his door and start shouting,

35:13.642 --> 35:17.143
“Oh, Mitterrand, Mitterrand, Mitterrand.”

35:24.017 --> 35:27.059
The police will arrest Me.

35:28.641 --> 35:32.226
I must take permission, I must have the protocol,

35:32.434 --> 35:34.684
I should be allowed to go inside,

35:34.892 --> 35:37.892
othewise it's not proper.

35:43.434 --> 35:45.059
In the same way if you say,

35:45.268 --> 35:48.309
if you take the name of anyone of the Deities,

35:48.518 --> 35:53.143
without Kundalini awakening, without proper protocol,

35:53.976 --> 35:56.642
the doors are closed. Not only that,

35:56.851 --> 36:01.226
but these chakras get spoilt, you get arrested.

36:14.351 --> 36:16.934
If it is with the president,

36:17.143 --> 36:20.184
I am talking about God All-mighty,

36:20.393 --> 36:23.767
who is the President of all the presidents.

36:31.601 --> 36:35.684
So, how can you do it? This is unauthorized.

36:52.642 --> 36:54.143
All right?

37:01.476 --> 37:04.059
Is it possible...?

37:17.226 --> 37:20.184
He's asking Mother, it's possible to be connected with the Divine,

37:20.351 --> 37:21.767
Is it possible?

37:21.934 --> 37:25.560
To be connected with the Divine without Kundalini awakening?

37:25.725 --> 37:32.351
No. You cannot create a tree without sprouting the seed.

37:43.434 --> 37:47.476
That’s what Christ has said: “Know thyself”.

37:51.641 --> 37:54.725
Without the Kundalini you cannot know yourself.

37:57.641 --> 38:03.101
This is described as the Tree of Life, in the Bible.

38:11.892 --> 38:15.101
What about Pranayama and Hatha Yoga?

38:16.601 --> 38:20.725
Pranayama is not going to help you, at all.

38:21.393 --> 38:24.641
Is a, you see, it's more physical.

38:24.892 --> 38:28.560
And we do pranayama, also, in Sahaja Yoga,

38:28.725 --> 38:33.017
but it is a very scientific, whenever it is necessary.

38:33.226 --> 38:39.226
Here the people do all these pranayama and all these yoga

38:39.892 --> 38:43.560
things as if taking all the medicines from the medicine-box,

38:43.725 --> 38:46.101
without a doctor.

39:08.601 --> 39:11.184
The best way to know is this way.

39:11.393 --> 39:14.809
You must have seen many people who are doing pranayama,

39:15.017 --> 39:16.934
who are doing yoga.

39:17.143 --> 39:19.309
What do you do, they do, when they run too much,

39:19.434 --> 39:21.101
what is it called in America?

39:21.226 --> 39:22.476
Jogging.

39:22.725 --> 39:25.851
Ha, they do jogging.

39:26.351 --> 39:29.434
Oh, they all run like mad, everybody runs.

39:29.641 --> 39:33.268
Everybody is running, all as if there's an earthquaqe,

39:33.351 --> 39:36.934
whether it is old, young, anything, everybody is running in America.

39:37.101 --> 39:40.560
So, anything you do,

39:41.393 --> 39:43.309
you must find out,

39:43.518 --> 39:47.934
what is the transformation that has come in that person?

40:13.809 --> 40:17.017
Is there, are they sweet people,

40:17.226 --> 40:21.143
are they joyous, are they peaceful?

40:25.268 --> 40:27.226
Hatha yogis are such that,

40:27.434 --> 40:29.851
if they come from this door, better run away from the other,

40:30.059 --> 40:33.059
the way they are horrid and hot temper.

40:36.268 --> 40:39.268
I know some.

40:40.725 --> 40:44.059
Mostly they divorce their wives, give up their children,

40:44.268 --> 40:47.351
there is no sweetness.

