Hitler was a Hatha Yogi, do you know that?

41:03.101 --> 41:06.309
And a follower of a Lama. Double.

41:07.184 --> 41:09.476
And a follower of a Lama.

41:22.934 --> 41:25.934
Not this one, another one.

41:26.143 --> 41:29.351
All right. There is another one gentleman asked.

41:29.601 --> 41:32.601
So you asked one question.

41:34.809 --> 41:36.393
What he is saying?

41:36.601 --> 41:39.017
He is asking what do you think of Bhakta Yoga?

41:39.226 --> 41:40.851
Hatha Yogi?

41:41.101 --> 41:43.059
Bhakti Yoga.

41:43.143 --> 41:46.017
Who is Bhakta Yogi, I don’t know. What do you think?

41:46.268 --> 41:49.976
Is the point.There are all kinds of bhakta, sakta, kata.

41:50.184 --> 41:52.934
But how am I to know all of them?

41:53.725 --> 41:58.767
Only thing I can say that you just see yourself.

41:59.184 --> 42:02.184
You can know yourself.

42:10.641 --> 42:13.934
You must know that Indians can be very cunning people,

42:14.143 --> 42:15.309
I’m sorry to say.

42:15.518 --> 42:20.184
Because we have had three hundred years the company of the English.

42:35.184 --> 42:39.725
Anything for which you have to pay, is all falsehood.

42:45.518 --> 42:48.641
That is as simple, very simple!

