How do we protect ourselves from negative vibrations, if we have?

43:31.393 --> 43:33.809
How do we protect ourselves from negative vibrations?

43:34.017 --> 43:36.851
That we’ll tell you everything,

43:37.059 --> 43:39.642
and we’ll be having a course.

43:41.642 --> 43:44.560
You’ll be expert.

43:44.725 --> 43:48.641
And no negative forces will come near you. They'll all run away.

43:53.059 --> 43:55.143
One day they'll run away from Paris

43:55.268 --> 43:57.309
and then from the whole of France.

44:26.641 --> 44:32.101
Let’s have it now. It’s there one more lady, there.

