Someone who doesn't know anything about Kundalini,

47:52.641 --> 47:53.892
can he get his Realization?

47:53.976 --> 47:58.642
Of course. That’s much better!

48:02.226 --> 48:05.976
That’s much better. Much better.

48:06.184 --> 48:08.934
That’s innocence.

48:09.143 --> 48:15.184
Those who know about it, are mostly very crooked people.

48:41.601 --> 48:44.393
They misuse it.

48:49.851 --> 48:52.601
They frighten people.

48:56.560 --> 49:00.226
Actually there is nothing to be known about Kundalini.

49:04.059 --> 49:07.976
But you see, you know French people, you cannot just ask them,

49:08.184 --> 49:09.725
to take their Realization.

49:09.934 --> 49:13.476
You have to tell them something about it, after all.

49:24.184 --> 49:26.934
Like, when you come in this room,

49:27.143 --> 49:30.767
if you have to put the lights, you just switch on one light.

49:31.101 --> 49:34.101
You don’t have to tell what is the history,

49:34.434 --> 49:38.560
how it came in, what is the source, you see.

49:39.143 --> 49:43.226
But, if it’s a French man, you may have to tell little bit.

50:06.767 --> 50:08.226
All right.

50:16.351 --> 50:18.892
There are two conditions.

50:19.143 --> 50:22.226
One condition is that,

50:22.434 --> 50:26.059
we are not to feel guilty at all, forget the past.

50:33.641 --> 50:38.976
Second condition is that you have to forgive everyone.

50:43.268 --> 50:45.767
Because both things are myths.

50:48.184 --> 50:51.976
Whether you forgive or don’t forgive, you don’t do anything.

50:56.851 --> 51:00.725
But if you don’t forgive, then you play into wrong hands.

51:06.934 --> 51:09.476
So don’t say it is difficult. Is the easiest thing to say,

51:09.642 --> 51:11.767
“I forgive”, everytime.

51:17.684 --> 51:20.434
Ones you forgive, the Divine takes over.

51:26.725 --> 51:30.101
So, you have to have these two conditions fulfilled.

51:36.017 --> 51:39.351
If you want to have Self-Realization,

51:39.601 --> 51:44.309
you all have to help to raise your Kundalini,

51:44.518 --> 51:46.101
as I'll tell you.

51:46.309 --> 51:49.017
But, if you don’t want to have, I cannot force you.

51:49.226 --> 51:53.226
It's in your freedom and in your glory, you have to get it.

52:08.184 --> 52:10.851
So all such people, if they don’t want,

52:11.059 --> 52:14.351
they can leave the hall, you cannot force.

52:26.641 --> 52:29.226
Now, we have to take the help of the Mother Earth,

52:29.434 --> 52:32.976
so if you don’t mind, you'll have to take out your shoes.

52:58.725 --> 53:01.518
And you have to sit comfortably,

53:01.684 --> 53:06.642
with both the legs, both the feet apart from each other.

53:15.642 --> 53:20.641
Tomorrow, tomorrow I will tell you more about the

53:20.851 --> 53:24.143
left and right channel, and two energies,

53:24.351 --> 53:29.518
but today remember, that left and right are two energies within us.

53:47.518 --> 53:52.143
So, we put our left hand like this, towards Me,

53:54.892 --> 53:59.560
and the right hand we have to use for the action.

54:00.725 --> 54:02.641
You come up, come.

54:02.809 --> 54:06.309
I'll stand up, I think. Can you put it up?

54:20.268 --> 54:24.059
First I will show you, then we'll have to close the eyes.

54:30.976 --> 54:34.518
You have to put your left hand towards Me like this.

54:39.143 --> 54:42.892
I think most of them got Realization in the music only.

54:52.560 --> 54:55.851
And the right hand we have to use for giving

54:56.059 --> 54:59.351
energy to our centers on the left hand side.

55:07.851 --> 55:12.767
So we put our left hand towards Me, like this,

55:12.976 --> 55:16.976
symbolizing our desire to get Realization.

55:25.017 --> 55:27.892
So right hand we put it on our heart.

55:30.351 --> 55:33.684
In the heart resides the Spirit,

55:36.892 --> 55:39.143
which is the reflection

55:39.351 --> 55:42.641
of God Almighty, the Creator, in our heart.

55:47.143 --> 55:49.560
Then we take down our right hand

55:49.725 --> 55:52.934
in the upper part of our abdomen.

55:58.851 --> 56:02.601
This is the center of our mastery.

56:06.601 --> 56:12.351
All the prophets and great masters have built this for us.

56:18.641 --> 56:20.560
Then we take down our right hand

56:20.725 --> 56:23.767
in the lower portion of our abdomen,on the left hand side.

56:31.809 --> 56:35.725
This is the center of pure knowledge,

56:38.642 --> 56:40.934
the pure knowledge that manifest

56:41.143 --> 56:43.601
through our central nervous system,

56:48.851 --> 56:51.476
beyond mental projections.

56:55.143 --> 56:58.892
Then we take our right hand in the upper part of our abdomen,

56:59.226 --> 57:01.725
on the left hand side, again.

57:05.268 --> 57:07.851
Then, onto our heart.

57:10.393 --> 57:14.143
Then we take our right hand in the corner of our shoulder

57:14.351 --> 57:19.184
and our neck, and we turn our head to our right.

57:27.767 --> 57:31.641
I think you also do it, otherwise everybody is watching.

57:31.892 --> 57:36.226
Now, so this is the center will catch, when we feel guilty.

57:42.560 --> 57:45.518
Now, we take this hand

57:45.684 --> 57:49.642
on our forehead across it, like this, across

57:49.851 --> 57:53.143
and press it on both the sides.

57:57.725 --> 58:01.560
We bend our head as, while we are pressing.

58:07.309 --> 58:10.434
This is the center for forgiveness.

58:13.767 --> 58:16.560
Then we take our hand on the back side of our head,

58:16.725 --> 58:21.226
and slowly move our head upward like this, allow it to rest.

58:28.809 --> 58:30.684
This is the center

58:31.017 --> 58:34.809
where we have to ask for forgiveness, without feeling guilty.

58:43.309 --> 58:46.518
Now, we spread our hand, stretch it,

58:46.684 --> 58:49.268
and put the center of our palm

58:49.560 --> 58:53.101
on top of our fontanel-bone area,

58:53.309 --> 58:56.642
which was a soft bone in our childhood.

59:00.351 --> 59:05.351
We bend our head and push back our fingers

59:05.560 --> 59:08.851
and press our scalp, hard,

59:09.059 --> 59:13.476
and move it slowly, seven times, clockwise.

59:30.518 --> 59:32.892
That’s all we'll have to do.

59:33.101 --> 59:36.309
Only thing, remember, don’t put hand from this side, put this way,

59:36.476 --> 59:39.892
and stretch your fingers quite a lot

59:40.101 --> 59:43.101
to bring pressure.

59:52.268 --> 59:56.184
This way, put it this way, from the front.

59:56.725 --> 59:59.684
Now, we’ll close your eyes.

59:59.892 --> 01:00:02.393
You can take out your spectacles, if you like.

01:00:09.017 --> 01:00:12.226
And we don’t open our eyes, till I tell you.

01:00:16.143 --> 01:00:17.809
All right.

01:00:18.059 --> 01:00:22.226
So now, please, put your right hand on your heart.

01:00:25.684 --> 01:00:31.226
Left hand towards Me, both the feet away from each other and now...

01:00:38.434 --> 01:00:42.393
Here you have to ask Me a very important question,

01:00:46.809 --> 01:00:51.642
”Mother, am I the Spirit?”

01:00:51.851 --> 01:00:54.017
Ask this questions three times.

01:01:04.684 --> 01:01:07.601
Now, if you are the Spirit,

01:01:07.809 --> 01:01:12.101
you are your master, you are your guide.

01:01:20.641 --> 01:01:23.268
So now, please, put your right hand

01:01:23.476 --> 01:01:26.601
in the upper portion of your abdomen.

01:01:31.059 --> 01:01:35.393
And, please, ask another question -

01:01:35.641 --> 01:01:39.767
you can call Me, Shri Mataji or Mother, whichever suits you -

01:01:47.976 --> 01:01:51.934
so please, ask the question

01:01:52.143 --> 01:01:57.434
“Mother, am I my own master?” Ask this question three times.

01:02:08.143 --> 01:02:10.725
I have already told you,

01:02:10.934 --> 01:02:14.560
that I cannot force pure knowledge on you.

01:02:14.725 --> 01:02:17.268
You have to know it in your own freedom,

01:02:17.476 --> 01:02:19.725
I respect your freedom.

01:02:33.809 --> 01:02:35.601
So please take your hand

01:02:35.767 --> 01:02:38.809
in the lower portion of your abdomen, on the left hand side

01:02:42.934 --> 01:02:45.767
and press it hard.

01:02:47.767 --> 01:02:49.809
Here,

01:02:51.851 --> 01:02:56.393
please, say: “Mother, give me pure knowledge!”

01:02:56.601 --> 01:03:00.226
I cannot force on you. Say it six times, because

01:03:00.434 --> 01:03:04.393
this center has got six petals or six sub-plexuses.

01:03:24.892 --> 01:03:27.226
As soon as you ask for pure knowledge,

01:03:27.476 --> 01:03:30.101
your Kundalini starts moving upward,

01:03:30.309 --> 01:03:35.101
so we have to support the centers with our

01:03:35.642 --> 01:03:38.684
full confidence, in the higher regions.

01:03:50.309 --> 01:03:52.725
So, please, raise your right hand

01:03:52.934 --> 01:03:56.641
in the upper portion of your abdomen, on the left hand side.

01:04:01.934 --> 01:04:05.393
Here, with full confidence, you have to say,

01:04:08.601 --> 01:04:11.309
ten times, ”Mother,

01:04:11.641 --> 01:04:16.143
I am my own master!” Say it ten times, please.

01:04:26.809 --> 01:04:28.976
Say it ten times.

01:04:33.725 --> 01:04:38.268
Now, we have to know, that we are not this body,

01:04:39.059 --> 01:04:43.851
we are not this mind, we are not this intellect.

01:04:53.641 --> 01:04:56.641
We are not these emotions,

01:04:58.226 --> 01:05:02.434
nor we are our conditionings, nor our ego.

01:05:05.351 --> 01:05:08.434
We are pure Spirit.

01:05:11.393 --> 01:05:16.434
So, please, raise your right hand to your heart,

01:05:16.641 --> 01:05:21.017
and say it with full confidence, twelve times,

01:05:21.226 --> 01:05:24.641
”Mother, I am the Spirit.”

01:05:55.560 --> 01:05:59.518
I have already told you, that

01:06:02.851 --> 01:06:06.059
we should not feel guilty at all.

01:06:15.017 --> 01:06:17.101
We have to know,

01:06:17.309 --> 01:06:25.184
that Divine is the ocean of Love and Compassion.

01:06:31.851 --> 01:06:39.226
It is the ocean of joy and bliss.

01:06:43.434 --> 01:06:49.767
But above all, it is the ocean of forgiveness.

01:06:53.518 --> 01:06:56.351
So whatever mistakes we commit,

01:07:00.684 --> 01:07:05.393
are dissolved into this great ocean of forgiveness.

01:07:09.434 --> 01:07:12.476
So, please, put your left hand

01:07:12.642 --> 01:07:17.560
in the corner of your neck and your shoulder,

01:07:17.725 --> 01:07:21.184
and turn your head to your right.

01:07:28.434 --> 01:07:30.518
Here...

01:07:31.226 --> 01:07:37.101
Here you have to say, with full confidence, sixteen times,

01:07:37.309 --> 01:07:39.601
sixteen times,

01:07:39.767 --> 01:07:44.601
”Mother, I am not guilty at all.”  Say it with full confidence.

01:08:03.309 --> 01:08:07.851
Now, as I have already told you,

01:08:09.434 --> 01:08:14.892
that whether we forgive or don't forgive, it is a myth.

01:08:22.434 --> 01:08:25.934
But if we don’t forgive, we play into wrong hands.

01:08:32.017 --> 01:08:35.143
And the Divinealso, says also,

01:08:35.351 --> 01:08:38.101
that " You better look after yourself".

01:08:43.059 --> 01:08:45.560
So, now, leave it to the Divine.

01:08:51.518 --> 01:08:54.642
Raise your right hand on your forehead

01:08:54.892 --> 01:08:59.309
and put the forehead, slowly bending down.

01:09:05.684 --> 01:09:08.725
Now, press it hard.

01:09:09.434 --> 01:09:14.101
Here, here you have to say,

01:09:14.351 --> 01:09:18.101
”Mother, I forgive everyone.” Please, do it. Because of this,

01:09:18.309 --> 01:09:21.851
I’ve seen many people, just don’t get Realization.

01:09:53.017 --> 01:09:56.934
Say it from your heart, not how many times.

01:10:01.059 --> 01:10:03.518
Now, take back your right hand

01:10:03.684 --> 01:10:06.226
on the back side of your head

01:10:06.434 --> 01:10:10.892
and put the head on it, slowly. Move it upward.

01:10:22.976 --> 01:10:26.476
Here now, you have to say without feeling guilty,

01:10:26.684 --> 01:10:30.809
without counting your mistakes, from your heart,

01:10:38.851 --> 01:10:43.101
“Oh, Divine, if I have done any mistakes, please, forgive me!”

01:10:51.017 --> 01:10:54.143
Now, say it from your heart.

01:11:00.601 --> 01:11:06.560
Stretch your hand, fully,

01:11:07.518 --> 01:11:10.017
and put the center of your palm

01:11:10.226 --> 01:11:13.809
on top of the fontanel bone area,

01:11:14.017 --> 01:11:17.560
which was a soft bone in your childhood.

01:11:23.725 --> 01:11:28.601
This is very important, because it is the actualization of baptism.

01:11:39.101 --> 01:11:45.767
Now, just push out your fingers

01:11:46.725 --> 01:11:51.518
and press your scalp hard,

01:11:51.809 --> 01:11:54.934
and move it seven times.

01:11:55.143 --> 01:12:00.017
But here, again, I cannot take your freedom.

01:12:00.351 --> 01:12:02.934
So, you have to say seven times,

01:12:03.226 --> 01:12:06.184
”Mother, please, give me my Realization!”

01:12:06.393 --> 01:12:10.434
I cannot force on you, I respect your freedom.

01:12:17.892 --> 01:12:20.309
Push back your fingers.

01:12:35.641 --> 01:12:38.976
It's quite in front, not on the back side, front side.

01:14:06.476 --> 01:14:09.725
Now, please, take down your hand.

01:14:09.934 --> 01:14:12.101
Have there been, more [unclear], it's all right.

01:14:12.309 --> 01:14:16.143
Now, see for yourself. Open your eyes slowly.

01:14:18.059 --> 01:14:20.642
Open your eyes slowly.

01:14:26.476 --> 01:14:31.892
Now, put your right hand towards Me,

01:14:32.641 --> 01:14:36.017
and bend your head and see from the left hand,

01:14:36.226 --> 01:14:38.351
if you are feeling the cool breeze

01:14:38.560 --> 01:14:43.268
coming out of your fontanel bone area, cool or hot.

01:15:00.143 --> 01:15:02.725
Now, please put your left hand

01:15:02.934 --> 01:15:06.518
and see with the right hand. Bend your head.

01:15:20.184 --> 01:15:24.226
Now, see with the right hand, again.

01:15:36.143 --> 01:15:39.268
Bend your head, bending down it's better.

01:15:46.393 --> 01:15:49.809
Now, raise your hands up like this

01:15:50.268 --> 01:15:55.059
and ask a question, three times,

01:15:55.309 --> 01:15:58.684
”Mother, is this the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost?

01:15:58.892 --> 01:16:03.934
Mother, is this the All-pervading power of God’s Love?

01:16:04.434 --> 01:16:06.560
Mother, is this the Brahmachaitanya?”

01:16:06.725 --> 01:16:09.934
Ask one of this, three times.

01:16:29.851 --> 01:16:32.601
Ask this, any of these questions, three times.

01:16:48.017 --> 01:16:52.393
All those, please, take down your hands.

01:16:55.309 --> 01:16:58.809
Now, watch Me without thinking. You can do it.

01:17:04.434 --> 01:17:07.476
Now, those who have felt the cool breeze

01:17:07.684 --> 01:17:13.101
out of their head, or in their hands, or even the heat,

01:17:13.434 --> 01:17:16.101
please, raise both your hands!

01:17:29.767 --> 01:17:35.143
Oh, My God! See the France. May God bless you all!

01:17:37.268 --> 01:17:40.351
So many of you!

01:17:40.601 --> 01:17:43.642
So be in silence now.

01:17:47.892 --> 01:17:50.393
Don’t argue.

01:17:52.476 --> 01:17:55.268
Tomorrow I’m coming again.

01:17:57.642 --> 01:18:00.809
If you all come early, then we can start the program

01:18:01.101 --> 01:18:03.351
at right time.

01:18:10.268 --> 01:18:14.725
And I would like to meet you all, personally, tomorrow.

01:18:18.976 --> 01:18:22.601
May God bless you all!

01:18:24.143 --> 01:18:26.725
So many of them have felt it.

01:18:31.309 --> 01:18:33.351
No one wants to leave.

01:18:43.226 --> 01:18:45.809
They are still here.

01:18:47.476 --> 01:18:49.934
They wait for Me to go....

01:18:52.268 --> 01:18:56.518
Some recording you can put, some musical record, anything.

01:18:58.226 --> 01:19:01.518
Any instrumental, so that…

01:19:15.268 --> 01:19:18.184
Tomorrow, tomorrow I'll be here.

01:19:19.725 --> 01:19:24.434
I’m saying just go and get if you can. Have some sort of a...

01:19:24.641 --> 01:19:28.059
Have you got some tape recordings? No tapes.

01:19:28.934 --> 01:19:32.226
Tapes? Have you got some musical tapes?

01:19:32.851 --> 01:19:37.476
No? You didn't bring any tapes, with you? Music tapes.

01:19:37.767 --> 01:19:39.725
Then [who comes out?].

01:19:43.684 --> 01:19:45.767
Where are My shoes?

01:20:12.268 --> 01:20:16.351
Patrick, also tell them, those who did not get Realization,

01:20:16.601 --> 01:20:20.476
should not feel disappointed. Tomorrow all of them will get it.

01:20:51.268 --> 01:20:56.143
Tomorrow you should bring because they understand [unclear].
